\section*{Evasion}
- change antigenicity
- stage specific, programmed (Trypanosomes), shedding
- resist effector mechanisms aimed at clearance
- ie. tegument is difficult to phagocytose
- sequester away from immune responses
- insides cells, in cysts, intestinal lumen
- induce T cell tolerance
- Tregs
